        " \"إِذَا كَانَ يَلْتَقِطُ غَيْرَ اَلْعَذِرَةِ فَلاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4150 - Zakariyya ibn Adam asked Abu al-Hasan (as) about water birds.\nImam (as) said: \"If they pick up things other than filth, then there is no harm in eating them.\""
        ]
